We watched citizens troop to political rallies in defiance of the Ministry of Health’s Covid-19 guidelines.Last year the PPEs that were donated to help deal with Covid-19 disappeared mysteriously while tenders for the procurement of the same were awarded to passers-by. Last year was no doubt the most difficult in recent times and the dawn of 2021 signified renewed hope. As the Covid-19 pandemic ravaged the country, the political class continued to dance to the political tunes, oblivious of the sufferings of their people. To them, the 2022 General Election and the referendum were more pressing concerns.



