We expect vaccines to be received this year. I cringe when I imagine that it is the same Kemsa that may be entrusted with the procurement and distribution of the vaccines.
Unless we hold the Covid-19 millionaires accountable, the vaccines will suffer the same fate. There is no magic in the number 2021. Whether or not it will be prosperous will purely depend on how we define our priorities as a nation.
